FeedPackage.Description:
Library which contains some basic, but so awesome classes:
1) Fast bit indexation class if you want to create back index for billions of persons or some other stuff, and want fast search among all of them.
2) Range tree. That's all it need's to say.
3) ConsoleTalker - it's better version of console, to talk to it, colorfully and thread safely. Also it provides interface to read generic (by default) and complex values (by your taste) without creating readers everywhere.
4) Some additional .NET logic what should be implemented but it is not. For example, deep equality of objects, ienumerable isEmpty(), etc.
FeedPackage.Title: AnotherBestClass
